    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows substantial wear, including several large dents, noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears in the seating and a non-functional infotainment system. Mechanically, the car starts but runs roughly, exhibiting a persistent check engine light and a noticeable leak from the transmission. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts, but it is not currently recommended for reliable daily use without major repairs.",
      "price": 8500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
