    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, reflecting its well-kept mechanical state. While there may be some minor signs of normal wear consistent with its age, the exterior and interior remain in great shape, making this a solid and trustworthy choice for its next owner. You can expect a comfortable drive and many more miles of service from this well-cared-for car.",
      "price": 37500.0,
