    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone who loves to get their hands dirty and bring a car back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical attention and some bodywork, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at a fraction of the cost. If you're looking for a rewarding restoration project, this is the one for you!",
